{"tid":500220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耀廷：2019區選讓泛民屆時拿下3、4百個議席 爭取2020年立法會過半議席","createTime":"2017-12-15T14:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T12:31:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8896a2318e8ade4ea2bc9ad52f709aace0a69701","tid":500220,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171215/57587309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57587309&d=%2FRaH1x5qWITByysv8wuJn26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b42e0561\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57587309&h=c5284d16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171215/57587309</a><br />\n<br />\n港大法律系副教授戴耀廷預告，未來打壓會陸續有來，但不用灰心。而拉布的確變難，但非不會發生，「議員可以發言講足15分鐘，把握機會問問題。消滅拉布係無可能！」他指，大家只要保持團結，是不會被消滅，呼籲泛民各組織要建立更緊密、更強大的政治聯盟，去抵抗威權。<br />\n戴耀廷估計，2019年將有300至400個泛民人士參選區議會，而每個要有10個義工幫助。他鼓勵泛民支持者踴躍參與和協助，讓泛民屆時拿下3、4百個議席，並爭取2020年立法會拿回過半議席。"},{"pid":"4a507f677d19510664565ccdc7f6272f6235e8c2","tid":500220,"uid":148639,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abb5a1580f819917f6adac8d261c0e5b7fa13f04","tid":500220,"uid":38472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:27:54.000Z","msg":"泛民依家轉變策略，專揭保蝗狗衰嘢好過啦"},{"pid":"a6eb7225fa7cfc500c1da2ca2792c69bcba89d16","tid":500220,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee9ad9f22a7f7302fcbeb21d976b7729f432fb4","tid":500220,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"戴妖幾時入去坐呀屌你老母<img src=\"/asset